    "echo": "feeling young on stage",
    "narrative": "Weekend physie competition photos arrived, capturing the joy of performing despite a psoriatic arthritis diagnosis eight years ago. The supportive community of women and weekly classes keep both joints mobile and spirits high. Dancing in front of crowds resurrects the professional dancer within, defying physical limitations. What began as Jason's encouragement four years ago has become essential self-care for this working single mum."
